These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  mechanic, designer, chef
1. the designer is on the far left##1
2. the mechanic is on the right of the chef##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Job   | designer | chef | mechanic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, analyst, manager
1. the manager is on the far right##1
2. the pilot is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Job   | pilot | analyst | manager |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, dancing, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Hobby   | card-games | dancing | skydiving |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, brazilian, turkish
1. the brazilian is on the far right##1
2. the brazilian is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality   | italian | turkish | brazilian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, fanta, juice
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |   3   |
| Beverage   | fanta | tea | juice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, bus, roller
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2  |  3   |
| Transport   | roller | bus | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, drama, horror
1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | mystery | drama |

